											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Custom anim of Karlach coming out excitedly, looking around, and trying to calm herself down, before walking giddily towards the party. Wyll walks in from the portal, looks around, sees the party, then breaks out of survival mode and loosens up with relief and gratitude, and walks proudly (subtly) towards the party., [DUPE] PLYR can reuse the animation of when they enter, look around, stop and take a deep breath before proceeding towards the party. &lt;Gwen Lee&gt;" />
